text: Giordano Mazzocchi (born on December 18, 1996) is an Italian musical artist and Internet personality.https://www.theonecelebrity.com/giordanomazzocchiHe is one of the Italy's inaugural celebrity version of Temptation Island, Temptation Island VIP with his reality star partner Nilufar Addati.https://www.chosic.com/similar-artists/giordano- mazzocchi/3nMnwaOd4MPONzv5i46Wza His journey began in 2017 in the entertainment, when he joined various Italian TV-shows. == Biography == Mazzocchi was born on December 18, 1996 in Viareggio in the region of Tuscany, Italy. ==Reference== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Italian musicians Category:Italian models
